author: Jesse Pound
title: New Jersey Gov. Phil Murphy says coronavirus numbers showing possible improvement
description: Social distancing measures seem to be effective in slowing the spread of the virus, Murphy said on CNBC's "Fast Money."
content:
New Jersey Gov. Phil Murphy said Monday that the state was starting to see positive signs that its social distancing policies were helping to curb the spread of the coronavirus.
